l us at +81 720 2212 to find out more details and let us know if you need a loan.</p></div></div></div><div class="item"><div class="boxmlthemeone31 textmlthemeone31"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-cke-saved-href="#detailsAccordion2" href="#detailsAccordion2" aria-expanded="false"><span class="circle-numbering">2</span><span class="accordion-title">It Will Take Up To 3 Days To Qualify Your Loan Request</span> <span class="editmlthemeone31">edit</span> <span class="savemlthemeone31">save</span> </a><div id="detailsAccordion2" class="collapse" data-parent="#detailsAccordion" role="tabpanel"><p class="accordion-body">After we've collected all the necessary data from you by phone and email for some documents, we send the loan request to our analysis department which usually answers in no more than 3 days.</p></div></div></div><div class="item"><div class="boxmlthemeone32 textmlthemeone32"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-cke-saved-href="#detailsAccordion3" href="#detailsAccordion3" aria-expanded="false"><span class="circle-numbering">3</span><span class="accordion-title">We'll Call You With The Answer From The Analysis Team</span> <span class="editmlthemeone32">edit</span> <span class="savemlthemeone32">save</span> </a><div id="detailsAccordion3" class="collapse" data-parent="#detailsAccordion" role="tabpanel"><p class="accordion-body">In most of the cases, if you don't have any bad credit history the loan will be 100% approved. Sometimes we ask for additional documents but it's a very rare situation when this happens.</p></div></div></div><div class="item"><div class="boxmlthemeone33 textmlthemeone33"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-cke-saved-href="#detailsAccordion4" href="#detailsAccordion4" aria-expanded="false"><span class="circle-numbering">4</span><span class="accordion-title">You Enjoy The Money Submitted To Your Bank Account</span> <span class="editmlthemeone33">edit</span> <span class="savemlthemeone33">save</span> </a><div id="detailsAccordion4" class="collapse" data-parent="#detailsAccordion" role="tabpanel"><p class="accordion-body">After a positive answer to your request analysis it usually takes no longer than 1 business day until you have the requested amount in your bank account. All this without going to a physical bank office.</p></div></div></div></div><!--{cke_protected}{C}%3C!%2D%2D%20end%20of%20detailsAccordion%20%2D%2D%3E--><!--{cke_protected}{C}%3C!%2D%2D%20end%20of%20accordion%20%2D%2D%3E--></div><!--{cke_protected}{C}%3C!%2D%2D%20end%20of%20col%20%2D%2D%3E--></div><!--{cke_protected}{C}%3C!%2D%2D%20end%20of%20row%20%2D%2D%3E--></div> <!--{cke_protected}{C}%3C!%2D%2D%20end%20of%20container%20%2D%2D%3E--></div><!--{cke_protected}{C}%3C!%2D%2D%20end%20of%20accordion%20%2D%2D%3E--><!--{cke_protected}{C}%3C!%2D%2D%20end%20of%20approval%20%2D%2D%3E--></section><div class="keditor-toolbar keditor-toolbar-component">   <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="keditor-ui btn-component-reposition"><i class="fa fa-arrows"></i></a>   <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="keditor-ui btn-component-duplicate"><i class="fa fa-files-o"></i></a>   <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="keditor-ui btn-component-delete"><i class="fa fa-times"></i></a></div></section></div>
